`,n.jsxs(e.p,{children:["To generate the images I need to have some back-end that is non-static and that I can easily call through some API. Several options exist, but for the moment I really like the system by ",n.jsx(e.a,{href:"https://cloud.ionos.de/managed/ai-model-hub",children:"Ionos"}),". It is a straight-forward API with several open source models for image generation like ",n.jsx(e.a,{href:"https://stability.ai/",children:"Stable Diffusion"})," or FLUX. The system is hosted in Europe, which I personally like these days and the costs are ok. You can get started within minutes on a local setup."]}),`
