`,n.jsxs(e.li,{children:[n.jsx(e.strong,{children:"Option A - Get public funding"}),": This comes attached with A LOT of strings, A LOT of administration and it is quite slow. It is nice to slowly expend out of your lab, but is not really adapted to get a startup of the ground."]}),`
